sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>(Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant REST as OVMS REST<br/>configurable/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as OVMS gRPC<br/>configurable/TCP gRPC
    participant OV as OpenVINO Runtime<br/>(in-process)
    participant GenAI as OpenVINO GenAI<br/>(in-process)
    participant S3 as S3 / Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Model Inference (REST via Platform Gateway)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (platform)
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward request<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    KRBAC->>REST: Forward to OVMS<br/>HTTP (localhost, plaintext)
    REST->>OV: Execute inference<br/>(in-process C++ API)
    OV-->>REST: Inference result
    REST-->>KRBAC: JSON response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: LLM Chat Completion (Streaming SSE)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>stream: true<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward<br/>HTTPS
    KRBAC->>REST: Forward<br/>HTTP
    REST->>GenAI: ContinuousBatchingPipeline<br/>(in-process)
    loop SSE Stream Tokens
        GenAI-->>REST: Generated token
        REST-->>KRBAC: SSE: data: {"choices":[...]}
        KRBAC-->>Gateway: SSE chunk
        Gateway-->>Client: SSE chunk (HTTPS)
    end
    REST-->>Client: SSE: data: [DONE]

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: gRPC Streaming Inference
    Client->>gRPC: ModelStreamInfer (bidirectional)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 (plaintext)
    gRPC->>OV: Execute inference<br/>(in-process)
    loop Streaming Response
        OV-->>gRPC: Partial result
        gRPC-->>Client: gRPC stream response
    end

    Note over Client,S3: Model Loading (Startup / Hot-reload)
    REST->>S3: GET model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / access keys
    S3-->>REST: Model files
    REST->>OV: Load model into OpenVINO
